  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An innovative survival horror imbued with the eternal brilliance of dungeon crawling</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a confined space with no escape, face relentless attacks from masked humans.  <br>Use your limited resources and wits to survive this desperate situation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple combat system with grid-based movement and free camera control. <br>   The only way to survive is to dodge dangers and defeat the approaching masked humans!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventurers must solve the mysteries hidden in the dungeon as they progress.  <br>Only true heroes, possessing both reason and courage, can reach the top of the tower!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/31c3fc22a16fd5ff5bfaf191e3396e7a.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Dungeon Exploration<br>Explore the ruins, find weapons and armor, and discover ways to survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/d88cea13d7c531eefa7fc3c7db972c09.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Strategic Combat<br>Grid-based movement is crucial for predicting enemy actions and positioning yourself to avoid attacks. Once cornered, there's no escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/864fd23f024c9c03e89f537e3e76392c.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Ancient Weapons<br>Use melee weapons like swords and spears to defeat fierce enemies. The power to save the world is in your hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3fb373a87f3805476261a60efa0209bd.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Elements and abilities <br>Players can allocate ability points through level-ups and equipment. It's up to you to decide which abilities to enhance.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4b4d962aeb1322c574668b725244ae07.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Difficult puzzles <br>Solve puzzles involving switches, pressure plates, and trapdoors. Items and a handy map feature will be helpful.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Words of the Unknown Brave:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/19f2593a643cfd2e815c10dbb20d46f2.avif?t=1756880554\" width=620 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this age where even legends are forgotten, <br>I heard an intriguing rumor about the Tower of Mask. <br>In that tower, which stands in a place unknown to people, there lurks an evil that heroes should challenge. <br>And those who step in are attacked by humans wearing bizarre masks. <br>I have never heard of anyone who returned safely from the tower. <br>Can I survive and escape from the tower...?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An innovative survival horror imbued with the eternal brilliance of dungeon crawling</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4888f8b6a892410230db5018f3b90bf4.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a confined space with no escape, face relentless attacks from masked humans.  <br>Use your limited resources and wits to survive this desperate situation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/42662ff6e5c4fb2aa0b9559ad49f74f5.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple combat system with grid-based movement and free camera control. <br>   The only way to survive is to dodge dangers and defeat the approaching masked humans!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.poster.avif?t=1756880554\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.webm?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3f2e1ed882a39bff8ae4d2109d9718ec.mp4?t=1756880554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventurers must solve the mysteries hidden in the dungeon as they progress.  <br>Only true heroes, possessing both reason and courage, can reach the top of the tower!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/31c3fc22a16fd5ff5bfaf191e3396e7a.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Dungeon Exploration<br>Explore the ruins, find weapons and armor, and discover ways to survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/d88cea13d7c531eefa7fc3c7db972c09.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Strategic Combat<br>Grid-based movement is crucial for predicting enemy actions and positioning yourself to avoid attacks. Once cornered, there's no escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/864fd23f024c9c03e89f537e3e76392c.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Ancient Weapons<br>Use melee weapons like swords and spears to defeat fierce enemies. The power to save the world is in your hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/3fb373a87f3805476261a60efa0209bd.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Elements and abilities <br>Players can allocate ability points through level-ups and equipment. It's up to you to decide which abilities to enhance.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/4b4d962aeb1322c574668b725244ae07.webp?t=1756880554\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Difficult puzzles <br>Solve puzzles involving switches, pressure plates, and trapdoors. Items and a handy map feature will be helpful.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/67d17e9df45616b4443d0b6cee4c29cf.webp?t=1756880554\" width=607 height=16 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Words of the Unknown Brave:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918410/extras/19f2593a643cfd2e815c10dbb20d46f2.avif?t=1756880554\" width=620 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this age where even legends are forgotten, <br>I heard an intriguing rumor about the Tower of Mask. <br>In that tower, which stands in a place unknown to people, there lurks an evil that heroes should challenge. <br>And those who step in are attacked by humans wearing bizarre masks. <br>I have never heard of anyone who returned safely from the tower. <br>Can I survive and escape from the tower...?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
